                    <introduction>

<assemblage>
  <title>Motivating Questions</title>
  <p>
  <statement>
	Here are some questions we'll consider.
	<ol>
	  <li>What is a direct proof?</li>
	  <li>What characteristics make for a good proof?</li>

	</ol>
